headline: Tyler Technologies (TYL) Soars 6.6%: Is Further Upside Left in the Stock?
summary: Tyler Technologies (TYL) witnessed a jump in share price last session on above-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions for the stock doesn't suggest further strength down the road.
